Text: MATH WEEK Good Afternoon Mr Kaminski This is just a brief reminder regarding the MATH WEEK conference agenda emailed to you on October th Have you received it If not the information can gladly be resent As you may be aware the conference is soon approaching November at the Millennium Conference Center in NYC It is important to submit your registration form via fax to ASAP Should you have any questions please call me at Ext Best Regards Grace Franklin
